## Africana Studies Relation

KBLA 1580 AM serves as a contemporary continuation of the tradition of Black-owned media that has historically provided a voice for the African-American community. Its focus on civil rights, economic empowerment, and cultural affirmation makes it an important subject of study within Africana Studies, highlighting the ongoing struggle for representation and equity in media.

